	* src/Extensions/Banshee.Lastfm/Banshee.Lastfm.Audioscrobbler/Queue.cs:
	* src/Extensions/Banshee.Lastfm/Banshee.Lastfm.Audioscrobbler/AudioscrobblerService.cs:
