2007-08-05  Aaron Bockover  <abock@gnome.org>

	0.13.0 Released

	* NEWS: Updated with 0.13.0 release notes

	* configure.ac: Do not check for cdparanoiasrc; cdda sources will be
	resolved at runtime via URI

