	* build/m4/banshee/dbus.m4:
	* build/Common.Makefile:
	* ext/dbus-sharp/Makefile.am:
	* configure.ac: Patch from Sebastian Dr√∂ge to allow linking against an
	external installation of NDesk DBus (BGO #409964)

