2006-10-23  Aaron Bockover  <abock@gnome.org>

	Patch by Scott Peterson, BGO #363548

	* src/Banshee.Base/Source.cs: Fix for ClearChildSources

	* src/Banshee.Plugins/Daap/DaapCore.cs:
