	search for when encoding to MP3 and no muxer was specified

	* src/banshee.in: Set GST_PLUGIN_PATH to $(libdir)/banshee/gstreamer-0.10
	to support loading private plugins (gstxing, gstdtdriver on SUSE/SLED)

