	* src/NotificationAreaIcon.cs: Removed

	* src/Banshee.Base/ActionManager.cs: 
	* src/PlayerInterface.cs: Removed tray-specific code 

	* src/Banshee.Base/Globals.cs: Added property to get handle to main window

