	* src/Banshee.Plugins/Audioscrobbler/AudioscrobblerPlugin.cs: 
	* src/Banshee.Plugins/Audioscrobbler/AudioscrobblerMenu.xml: Added a
	visit group action to the menu and changed menu items to sentence case

