2005-11-12  Aaron Bockover  <aaron@aaronbock.net>

	* data/images/source-cd-audio.png: Updated with tango icon
	* src/IpodCore.cs (IpodMisc.GetIcon): Accept either an Ipod.Device or
	an Ipod.DeviceModel
