	* src/AudioCdCore.cs: Fetch cover art from Amazon.com after MusicBrainz 
	returns an ASIN
	* src/PlayerInterface.cs: Show a CoverArtThumbnail widget in header
	* src/LibraryTrackInfo.cs: Copy ASIN from AudioCdTrackInfo to 
	LibraryTrackInfo
