	* configure.in: Version 0.9.7
	* configure.in: Require ipod-sharp 0.5.4
	* src/IpodCore.cs: Disabled status, some kind of LTM bug... looking into it
	* src/IpodPropertiesWindow.cs: Fixed NullRef bug
